item.title: OpenOffice.org: vmiklos01 CWS integrated
item.description: Once I was ready with this year’s GSoC work I started to submit it back to OpenOffice.org. Before that was completed, LibreOffice was launched, though I thought if I started working on submitting it to OpenOffice.org as well, I’ll finish it. About 6 weeks later they now integrated (merged) the vmiklos01 CWS (the branch containing my GSoC work) to DEV300, what will became OpenOffice.org 3.4 later.
item.dc:creator: Miklos Vajna
